"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1931223-Olympics-2024-Village-bottled-water-heat\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  There is reportedly a shortage of bottled water available to staff and athletes inside theOlympicVillage as another issue in Paris comes to the surface.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999067094948, \"rank\": 9.32905692298476e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes' base has split opinion among sports stars in years gone by, with tennis aceCoco Gauffthe latest star to speak out against the facility after claiming that 10 women were forced to share two bathrooms.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reports of a shortage in eggs and meat emerged earlier this week, two staples of an athletes' diet - in most cases - given the need for protein.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it is not just food which is said to be running low at the sporting hub.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theDaily Mail, there is now a shortage of bottled water in the Village and staff have been forced to 'ration' the supplies and what they can give out to ensure that they have enough to get through the next few days of immense heat.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The temperatures in the French capital have been blistering throughout the competition so far, pushing athletes to their very limits when competing.\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9946209606025329, \"rank\": 0.005383649122811426, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \